   LONDON
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
KWU, the Siemens power engineering business, has formed a joint venture with
companies of the Russian ministry of nuclear energy to engineer and market
control and instrumentation systems for nuclear power plants, writes Andrew
Baxter in London.
